    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class=" col-md-6">
                <div>
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="images/security.jpg" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" col-md-6">
                <div class="story_detail">
                    <h3>
                        Our
                    </h3>
                    <h2>
                        Success Stories
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page
                        when
